## Sprint Ceremonies

### Sprint Planning
1. Load `@BMAD/_bmad/bmm/workflows/4-implementation/sprint-planning/`
2. Review backlog
3. Estimate stories
4. Commit to sprint goal

### Daily Standup
- What did I complete?
- What will I work on?
- Any blockers?

### Sprint Review
- Demo completed work
- Gather feedback
- Update backlog

### Retrospective
1. Load `@BMAD/_bmad/bmm/workflows/4-implementation/retrospective/`
2. What went well?
3. What to improve?
4. Action items

